supportDesc.foliation: Modern foliation in pencil appears on every tenth leaf (1, 11, 21, etc.). Beginning with folio 1711, which is incorrectly labeled as 1721, the foliation is misnumbered by ten leaves. Consequently, Gödel’s total of 1,903 leaves is incorrect.
